criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with common bile duct stone underwent successful stone removal by ERCP in
             Xijing Hospital of Digestive Diseases.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Gallbladder stones or hepatolithiasis;

          -  Stenosis of biliary duct;

          -  Incomplete common bile duct stone removal by ERCP;

          -  Common bile duct stent;

          -  Unable to provide informed consent.
